Package: mmflowr
Type: Package
Title: A package for enumeration and assignment in transportation modeling
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Kamol", "Roy", email = "kamol.roy08@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: MMFlowR is an R package for transportation modeling, specifically designed for enumeration 
    and assignment tasks in network analysis. It provides tools for analyzing traffic flow, route 
    optimization, and transportation network modeling.
